.                     START
                      │
                      ▼
             Initialize ESP32
                      │
                      ▼
        Initialize MQ-2, DHT11,
      RGB LED, Buzzer & Bluetooth
                      │
                      ▼
         Read MQ-2 Gas Sensor Value
                      │
                      ▼
      Read Temperature & Humidity
             from DHT11 Sensor
                      │
                      ▼
         Compare Gas Value with
          Predefined Thresholds
                      │
          ┌───────────┼───────────┐
          ▼           ▼           ▼
        SAFE      MODERATE     DANGER
          │           │           │
 Green LED ON   Yellow LED ON  Red LED ON
 Short Beep     Medium Beep    Long Beep
          │           │           │
          └───────────┼───────────┘
                      ▼
      Display Data on Serial Monitor
      (CSV Format with Timestamp)
                      │
                      ▼
      Send Alert to Mobile via
      Bluetooth (if Warning/Danger)
                      │
                      ▼
            Wait 2 Seconds
                      │
                      ▼
               Repeat Loop
